columnTypes.name: bin
columnTypes.description: Indexing field to speed chromosome range queries

columnTypes.name: name
columnTypes.description: Name of gene (usually transcript_id from GTF)

columnTypes.name: txStart
columnTypes.description: Transcription start position (or end position for minus strand item)

columnTypes.name: txEnd
columnTypes.description: Transcription end position (or start position for minus strand item)

columnTypes.name: cdsStart
columnTypes.description: Coding region start (or end position for minus strand item)

columnTypes.name: cdsEnd
columnTypes.description: Coding region end (or start position for minus strand item)

columnTypes.name: exonStarts
columnTypes.description: Exon start positions (or end positions for minus strand item)

columnTypes.name: exonEnds
columnTypes.description: Exon end positions (or start positions for minus strand item)

columnTypes.name: cdsStartStat
columnTypes.description: Status of CDS start annotation (none, unknown, incomplete, or complete)

columnTypes.name: cdsEndStat
columnTypes.description: Status of CDS end annotation (none, unknown, incomplete, or complete)

columnTypes.name: exonFrames
columnTypes.description: Reading frame of the start of the CDS region of the exon, in the direction of transcription (0,1,2), or -1 if there is no CDS region.

longLabel: AUGUSTUS ab initio gene predictions v3.1
